data: {"id":"066bf5eec3c5afb602e74ebfbcfec6e8","choices":[{"finish_reason":"stop","index":0,"message":{"content":"# How to Make a Peanut Butter Sandwich\n\n**Ingredients:**\n- 2 slices of bread\n- Peanut butter (creamy or crunchy)\n- Optional: jelly, honey, or banana\n\n**Steps:**\n\n1. **Get your ingredients** — Gather 2 slices of bread, a jar of peanut butter, and any spreads you'd like.\n\n2. **Open the bread bag** — Remove two slices and set them on a clean plate or cutting board.\n\n3. **Open the peanut butter jar** — Unscrew the lid and set it aside.\n\n4. **Grab a knife** — Use a butter knife or table knife for spreading.\n\n5. **Scoop peanut butter** — Dip the knife into the jar and pull out a generous amount.\n\n6. **Spread on first slice** — Lay one bread slice flat and spread the peanut butter evenly across it. Start from the center and work outward.\n\n7. **Add toppings (optional)** — If using jelly, honey, or banana, add them now on top of the peanut butter.\n\n8. **Add the second slice** — Place the other bread slice on top, peanut-butter side down.\n\n9. **Press gently** — Push down lightly so the sandwich holds together.\n\n10. **Cut (optional)** — Cut diagonally or straight down the middle for easier eating.\n\n11. **Enjoy!** — Eat right away or wrap in foil for later.\n\n**Tips:**\n- If the bread tears, use a fresh slice.\n- Room-temperature peanut butter spreads more easily.\n- Store-bought bread works best when fresh.","role":"assistant","name":"MiniMax AI","audio_content":"","reasoning_content":"The user wants step-by-step instructions for making a peanut butter sandwich. I'll provide clear, simple instructions.","reasoning_details":[{"type":"reasoning.text","id":"reasoning-text-1","format":"MiniMax-response-v1","index":0,"text":"The user wants step-by-step instructions for making a peanut butter sandwich. I'll provide clear, simple instructions."}]}}],"created":1780269806,"model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","object":"chat.completion","usage":{"total_tokens":372,"total_characters":0,"prompt_tokens":31,"completion_tokens":341,"completion_tokens_details":{"reasoning_tokens":24}},"input_sensitive":false,"output_sensitive":false,"input_sensitive_type":0,"output_sensitive_type":0,"output_sensitive_int":0,"base_resp":{"status_code":0,"status_msg":""}}

